{"id":"q021","question":"嵌入失败时记录的 failure_state 标识值是什么？","expected_answer_keywords":["failure_state","EMBEDDING_FAILED"],"source":"knowledge/pdf/ingestion_recovery_manual.pdf","category":"identifier","evidence":[{"source":"knowledge/pdf/ingestion_recovery_manual.pdf","quote":"failure_state = EMBEDDING_FAILED","page":1,"section":null,"heading_path":[]}],"annotation_rationale":"该题验证恢复手册第一页的精确状态标识值。","tests_structured_chunking":false,"relevant_chunk_ids":["8f492102b554d59c62bdef71bb74ffd1ab48a02d373b7a6f2daf503969a5737a"],"relevant_chunk_ids_by_strategy":{"recursive":["4f45ef92210d99f8f4f7cc5da9eb5e65fc53746ecf2b9cb87c1bd899e4c27d71"],"pdf_page_aware":["8f492102b554d59c62bdef71bb74ffd1ab48a02d373b7a6f2daf503969a5737a"]}}
{"id":"q022","question":"一次失败的摄取从记录故障、复用重试标记到最终验证完成，应执行哪些关键检查？","expected_answer_keywords":["document ID","failed batch index","INGEST_RETRY_TOKEN","same embedding model","stored chunk count","source page metadata"],"source":"knowledge/pdf/ingestion_recovery_manual.pdf","category":"procedure","evidence":[{"source":"knowledge/pdf/ingestion_recovery_manual.pdf","quote":"Operators should record the document ID, failed batch index, and source filename before retrying.","page":1,"section":null,"heading_path":[]},{"source":"knowledge/pdf/ingestion_recovery_manual.pdf","quote":"Reuse this token for every retry of the same failed ingestion attempt.","page":2,"section":null,"heading_path":[]},{"source":"knowledge/pdf/ingestion_recovery_manual.pdf","quote":"The values must match for the recovered document.","page":3,"section":null,"heading_path":[]}],"annotation_rationale":"过程题按手册三页串联故障记录、重试和验证，答案必须保持页面阶段顺序。","tests_structured_chunking":true,"relevant_chunk_ids":["8f492102b554d59c62bdef71bb74ffd1ab48a02d373b7a6f2daf503969a5737a","d2d54b17f36facc321d72dda1cf62500d8ada88aea61595b1fee173b0caf79bf","6cde23a9fa53a879b4c83a83833af028ca8e41418e7c7417046928e331a000a2"],"relevant_chunk_ids_by_strategy":{"recursive":["4f45ef92210d99f8f4f7cc5da9eb5e65fc53746ecf2b9cb87c1bd899e4c27d71","1d3f24ce40c921348552054ef172bd10ac1dfef9f6f8737fb397962a96bbd30d","4905b01d451ed693e7aafb4f0470cb77f1f5fa2981c078ebdfd9edc00d7ff499"],"pdf_page_aware":["8f492102b554d59c62bdef71bb74ffd1ab48a02d373b7a6f2daf503969a5737a","d2d54b17f36facc321d72dda1cf62500d8ada88aea61595b1fee173b0caf79bf","6cde23a9fa53a879b4c83a83833af028ca8e41418e7c7417046928e331a000a2"]}}
{"id":"q023","question":"恢复原失败摄取与创建新摄取表示的边界是什么？","expected_answer_keywords":["same embedding model","vector dimension","chunk strategy","chunk size","overlap","new ingestion representation"],"source":"knowledge/pdf/ingestion_recovery_manual.pdf","category":"comparison","evidence":[{"source":"knowledge/pdf/ingestion_recovery_manual.pdf","quote":"A retry must use the same embedding model, vector dimension, chunk strategy, chunk size, and overlap. Changing these parameters starts a new ingestion representation rather than recovering the failed one.","page":2,"section":null,"heading_path":[]}],"annotation_rationale":"第二页明确列出恢复所需不变量，并与新表示的触发条件形成对比。","tests_structured_chunking":true,"relevant_chunk_ids":["d2d54b17f36facc321d72dda1cf62500d8ada88aea61595b1fee173b0caf79bf"],"relevant_chunk_ids_by_strategy":{"recursive":["1d3f24ce40c921348552054ef172bd10ac1dfef9f6f8737fb397962a96bbd30d"],"pdf_page_aware":["d2d54b17f36facc321d72dda1cf62500d8ada88aea61595b1fee173b0caf79bf"]}}
{"id":"q024","question":"判定 INGEST_RETRY_TOKEN 恢复完成时，检索结果和存储元数据必须满足什么条件？","expected_answer_keywords":["relevant page 2 chunk","stored chunk count","source page metadata","RECOVERY_COMPLETE"],"source":"knowledge/pdf/ingestion_recovery_manual.pdf","category":"citation","evidence":[{"source":"knowledge/pdf/ingestion_recovery_manual.pdf","quote":"Recovery is complete only when the relevant page 2 chunk is returned and the stored chunk count plus source page metadata checks both pass.","page":3,"section":null,"heading_path":[]},{"source":"knowledge/pdf/ingestion_recovery_manual.pdf","quote":"verification_status = RECOVERY_COMPLETE","page":3,"section":null,"heading_path":[]}],"annotation_rationale":"问题要求引用第三页的完成判据与最终状态，页码本身也是答案的一部分。","tests_structured_chunking":true,"relevant_chunk_ids":["6cde23a9fa53a879b4c83a83833af028ca8e41418e7c7417046928e331a000a2"],"relevant_chunk_ids_by_strategy":{"recursive":["4905b01d451ed693e7aafb4f0470cb77f1f5fa2981c078ebdfd9edc00d7ff499"],"pdf_page_aware":["6cde23a9fa53a879b4c83a83833af028ca8e41418e7c7417046928e331a000a2"]}}
